      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Fine-tuning is the right choice only after prompt-level fixes and few-shot injection have plateaued. The signal quality bar is high: a fine-tuning dataset with noise trains the model to reproduce that noise reliably."
          }
        ]
